      <title>印度尼西亚将在货币决策繁忙的一周维持关键利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/indonesia-to-hold-key-rate-in-busy-week-for-monetary-decisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚央行可能会连续第五个月维持基准利率不变，以支持卢比，在美国货币宽松政策变得更加明确之前，政策制定者不太可能采取行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/indonesia-to-hold-key-rate-in-busy-week-for-monetary-decisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
