    <item>
      <title>柯里称油价将突破美联储降息共识</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/commodities-are-set-to-rally-further-if-fed-cuts-currie-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯雷投资集团 (Carlyle Group LP) 的杰夫·柯里 (Jeff Currie) 表示，如果美联储在未来几个月降息，油价将上涨至远高于当前共识观点的每桶 70 至 90 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/commodities-are-set-to-rally-further-if-fed-cuts-currie-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 21:05:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
